Hello! In this page you can find sources to some Autonomous Templates!
Feel free to use these however you like!



###Example
Below is a very simple autonomous to use as an example:
```
...//other code generated by template
task main()
{
  initializeRobot();

  waitForStart();
  
  motor[Left] = 100;
  motor[right] = 100;
  wait1Msec(5000);
  motor[Left] = 0;
  motor[right] = 0;

...//other code generated by template
```

There is more where that came from in our template files!
